data.description: This enchanting log cabin offers panoramic views, thoughtful upgrades & an ideal location! Boasting 3 bedrooms & 2 bathrooms, this home is nestled on 1.14 acres of usable land, providing  space for a garden, shop, or outdoor entertainment. The covered front porch is perfect for soaking in the mountain air & watching the elk & deer roam the property. Enjoy year-round comfort with central air, electric forced air, a 2-year-old pellet stove (including approx 5 tons of pellets) & a generator-ready setup. The property has been expanded w/ an attached 2 car garage  Plus 288 sq ft added by the Seller since county records were updated. Garage is full insulation w/ generous space for tools & toys..   RV parking with plug-ins is located behind the garage & a new main water line with frost-free has been installed. HOA fees cover access to private geothermal pool and road maintenance. Community Water.  The home comes furnished, ensuring a seamless move-in experience!
